OL,4,G0000FMud Mountain Haulers
OL,5,     GTrouble on the traction line
OL,6,     Gleaves Craig frustrated by
OL,7,     Gendless breakdowns; a driver
OL,8,     Gfights a back injury to keep the
OL,9,     Gtrucks moving and a log hauler's
OL,10,     Gcrash sparks an all-night rescue.
OL,11,G0100FOutback Truckers
OL,12,     GA driver travels through an area
OL,13,     Gwhere bush fire has run wild. An
OL,14,     Gowner operator faces the busiest
OL,15,     Gweek of his career.
OL,16,G0200FTrucking Hell
OL,17,     GWhen a driver transporting booze
OL,18,     Gdecouples at a lorry park, his
OL,19,     Gtrailer's landing legs are
OL,20,     Gswallowed by some porous tarmac.
OL,21,     GThe recovery pushes Jordan and
OL,22,     GMerrie's skills to the limit.
